N:skill-standardization
D:Standardize and validate SKILL.md files against the Agent Skills specification (agentskills.io). Use when creating new skills, auditing existing skills for spec compliance, converting legacy formats, or improving descriptions for reliable triggering. Triggers on: validate skill, create SKILL.md, standardize skill format, check skill spec, improve skill description.
G:skill-management standardization validation agentskills-spec automation description-optimization
U[6]:
  Creating a new SKILL.md from scratch
  Auditing existing skills for spec compliance
  Converting legacy skill formats to standard structure
  Improving descriptions for better triggering accuracy
  Adding evaluation test cases (evals/evals.json)
  Batch-validating all skills in a directory
S[3]{n,action}:
  1,Validate skill with scripts/validate_skill.sh
  2,Create or fix SKILL.md frontmatter and sections
  3,Write effective description with imperative phrasing and trigger keywords
